Package: strobe
Title: Tools for STROBE-Style Inclusion and Exclusion Tracking with patient-level data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Vagish", "Hemmige", email = "vahemmig@montefiore.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions for tracking inclusion and exclusion criteria 
    in observational cohort studies when working directly with patient-level data, inspired by 
    the STROBE (Strengthening the Reporting of Observational Studies in Epidemiology) framework. 
    Functions support initializing a tracking object, logging filters and exclusions, and 
    generating flow diagrams compatible with publication standards.
